summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting easements for sanitary sewer purposes over Lots 1 and 2, Block 2, Lake Washington Shorelands, and over Lots 9 and 10, Block 28, Laurelhurst Addition (Being portions of Parcels A and B of short Plat 76-149) and releasing an easement in lieu thereof.
